# 🚨 AI Vendor Payment Anomaly Detector

**Built by Ashok Sharma** | SAP FICO Auditor (17+ years FMCG & Manufacturing)

**Live Demo**: [https://aiauditengineer.onrender.com/](https://aiauditengineer.onrender.com/)

A production-grade AI tool that turns any SAP FICO / Caseware IDEA export into instant high-risk transaction flags with **plain-English SHAP explanations**.

### Features
- Upload any CSV/Excel vendor payment file
- Isolation Forest + XGBoost anomaly detection
- SHAP-based audit-ready explanations (e.g., “341.5× historical average”)
- Interactive filters, Plotly charts, metric cards
- SQLite audit trail + automatic weekly GitHub Actions run
- Fully deployed on Render (free tier)

### Tech Stack
Python • Streamlit • Scikit-learn • XGBoost • SHAP • Plotly • GitHub Actions • SQLite

### How to Run Locally
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/AI-Audit-Engineer-Portfolio.git
cd AI-Audit-Engineer-Portfolio
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py

Built as part of my 12-week AI Audit Engineer roadmap — moving from traditional sampling audits to 100% population testing with explainable AI.
